comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Hood (UTA) landed OOB while in contact with the ball. The ruling on the court was overturned and Charlotte was awarded possession.
Batum (CHA) makes incidental contact with Booker (UTA) during rebounding.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Lin (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) briefly engages with Williams (CHA) during rebounding.
Zeller (CHA) makes contact with Hayward's (UTA) arm that affects his driving layup attempt.
Hayward (UTA) makes incidental contact with Walker (CHA) that causes him to fall to the floor as he attempts to get open during the inbounds play.
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Batum (CHA).
Hayward (UTA) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
Gobert (UTA) does not establish a legal guarding position and makes contact with Batum (CHA) as he hedges after the screen.
Lin (CHA) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Hood's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Burke (UTA) makes contact with Lin (CHA) that affects his RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Zeller's (CHA) arm that affects his layup attempt.
RHH shows that Walker (CHA) makes contact with Hayward's (UTA) arm that affects his driving layup attempt.
Burke (UTA) obtains a legal guarding position at the start of Lin's (CHA) drive.
Booker (UTA) clamps the arm of Williams (CHA), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
RHH shows that Zeller (CHA) cleanly strips the ball from Hayward (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) grabs Walker's (CHA) arm after he secures the loose ball.
Lin (CHA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Hood's (UTA) drive.
L-SLA shows that Lin (CHA) makes contact with the ball causing Booker (UTA) to bobble it prior to his shot attempt.
Batum (CHA) grabs and holds Hayward (UTA) affecting his ability to cleanly catch the inbounds pass.
Zeller (CHA) grabs and holds Gobert (UTA) affecting his ability to catch the inbounds pass.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Lin (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Hood (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hood (UTA) avoids Walker (CHA) while contesting the jump shot attempt.
Hayward (UTA) briefly engages with Batum (CHA) on the inbound pass.
Hayward (UTA) steps OOB while in possession of the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Hayward (UTA) stepped OOB while in possession of the ball was confirmed.
Booker (UTA) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
Hayward (UTA) makes incidental contact with Batum (CHA) as he intercepts the inbounds pass.
Booker (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Walker (CHA) during the inbounds play.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Batum (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Zeller (CHA) sets the back screen on Hood (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Walker (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact. Gobert then makes incidental contact with Walker as he rolls to the basket.
Burke (UTA) makes incidental contact with Lin (CHA) that does not affect his RSBQ as he fights over the screen.
Hayward (UTA) cleanly strips the ball from Batum (CHA) prior to any incidental contact with his arm.
PXP shows that Booker (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Williams (CHA) during the inbounds play. The two make incidental contact with one another and Williams falls to the floor.
Burke (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Walker's (CHA) drive and shot attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Walker.
Zeller (CHA) jumps vertically and then cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt by Booker (UTA).
Zeller (CHA) makes incidental contact with Gobert (UTA) in transition.
LHH shows that Burke (UTA) cleanly blocks Walker's (CHA) driving layup attempt.
Zeller (CHA) pushes Burke (UTA) affecting his ability to save the ball from going OOB.
Batum (CHA) makes incidental contact with Hayward (UTA) that does not affect his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Hood (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Booker (UTA) sets the screen on Lin (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Williams (CHA) extends his left arm into Gobert's (UTA) face on the driving layup attempt.
Zeller (CHA) does not obtain a legal guarding position and makes contact with Hayward's (UTA) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) makes incidental contact with Burke (UTA) during rebounding.
[Observable in enhanced video] Zeller (CHA) is not in possession of the ball when he steps OOB.
Burke (UTA) cleanly knocks the ball away from Lin (CHA).
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Zeller's (CHA) arm on the play to the basket.
Booker (UTA) makes contact with Zeller's (CHA) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
Walker (CHA) makes contact with Burke (UTA) that affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Burke (UTA) was behind the three point line when he was fouled by Walker (CHA) was confirmed.
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
